{"type": "article", "id": 14824, "title": "抓住秋天最后爱一下T恤，给你推荐这7个品牌", "description": "它们的共同特点是：让你看起来像个轻松的有钱人。", "date": "2015-09-14T09:15:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4711, "name": "T-shirt"}, {"id": 9210, "name": "Brandy Melville"}, {"id": 15938, "name": "Area"}, {"id": 15939, "name": "Evelane"}, {"id": 15940, "name": "Alternative Apparel"}, {"id": 15941, "name": "Oak"}, {"id": 15942, "name": "James Perse"}, {"id": 15943, "name": "T by Alexander Wang"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 248, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021054545e9ZaSlorwzgnONd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">T-shirt  是衣橱里的必备款，能搭配牛仔裤，套西装外套，还能从夏天穿到秋天。最重要的是 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">T-shirt  还能</span>多式样混搭，出镜率极高又耐穿。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">那么，平时，你在哪里买 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">T-shirt </span>呢？不会淘宝 100 元三件吧，还是转角就去了<span style=\"text-align:start;\">H&amp;M、Uniqlo、或者是 Zara？总有人觉得这种东西穿一个夏天就好，其实越是基本款，对质感的要求就越高。除了造型，更重要的是棉质，洗了三回以内就懈了的，那基本上可以排除在采购范围之外。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"text-align:start;\">这里有几个品牌，你也许可以选择：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.brandymelvilleusa.com/clothing/tops/tees.html\">Brandy Melville</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/8747.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span></a><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/8747.html\" target=\"_blank\">我们曾经也写过</a>这个 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">1994 年成立于意大利的品牌</span>。<a href=\"http://www.brandymelvilleusa.com/clothing/tops/tees.html\">Brandy Melville</a> 以它的<span style=\"text-align:start;\">小上衣、高腰裤、宽松毛衣而闻名。除此之外，还有它著名的少女风<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> Instagram 营销。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105439eFoO6mXcuSlCw7NB.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1071\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.99166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105439NoKnMpvJdjgchGDE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1078\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.99814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105440k8nRs7FqQ1hPKYbC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105440l0Ow9FTSGuPY8da7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://area.nyc/\">Area</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t设计师曾为<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> Chloe、Calvin Klein 工作。设计有中性风和立体剪裁。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105441Fb5GJDgZ4o9fy1N7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105441Ekbd8rLsjc2qHoyW.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1534\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.42037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105442CZIyWmBXwxrHp0Tz.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.everlane.com/\">Evelane</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t2010 年创立的 <a href=\"http://www.everlane.com/\">Evelane</a>，大部分时间是以它线上销售的商业模式而著名。不过，它的简洁设计也有美感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105442bc5UfZLIxFaOMS9e.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1362\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.26111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105443XS5WyO0wJCtgjEir.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1362\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.26111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105443NZPYgjRhdmW4uHSz.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1362\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.26111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021054448Pr9oaIUNO5HGRb1.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1362\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.26111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.alternativeapparel.com/womens-clothing/tops/t-shirts?utm_source=pepperjam&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=21181\">Alternative Apparel</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.alternativeapparel.com/womens-clothing/tops/t-shirts?utm_source=pepperjam&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=21181\">Alternative Apparel</a> 成立于 1996 年，创办人 Greg Alterman 在自己的车子里卖所设计的衣服。这个品牌是各路明星扮低调时候的爱。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105444v6Je0xwaCWuUFmhR.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105445kPhiglsY30yvRrXj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105445GRgQdUWm7XtxHz2w.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105445p6SYQOUc9AnT5sHw.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.oaknyc.com/women/oak-collection/tees.html\">Oak</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t来自纽约的<span style=\"text-align:start;\">时装独立</span><a href=\"http://www.china-ef.com/brand/\" target=\"_blank\">品牌</a>，擅长不对称设计和宽松的简约设计。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105446arOhF4NjMWs6QIzb.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1427\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.3212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105446XRd4WyDLVw9USfhm.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1427\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.3212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021054471vM3XR5h7glYKwnj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1427\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.3212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021054473MzySriRBYVO5DQt.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1427\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.3212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.jamesperse.com/women/apparel/t-shirts?ranMID=39476&amp;ranEAID=TnL5HPStwNw&amp;ranSiteID=TnL5HPStwNw-hNsvYAtcxrCsK8Lf7hv6mQ&amp;cm_mmc=Affiliate-_-Linkshare-_-10-_-1TnL5HPStwNw-hNsvYAtcxrCsK8Lf7hv6mQ\">James Perse</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t来自洛杉矶的品牌，以休闲装出名。因为《绯闻女孩》的 Queen B 在剧中穿着而走红。设计师 James Perse 的设计灵感来自于南加州的休闲风情。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105448GIWJ7jelXKBYzxo6.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105449Ue1spvibTXZzO4Nc.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105450DX0rp4WPVyUEOzjw.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105450UZ7bqiPyVSmec60f.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105451pzRkSMI4mON53fJg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105451KuT1Ea3ACd5wxOHh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.alexanderwang.com/us/shop/t-by-alexander-wang/women/t-by-alexander-wang/tops?utm_campaign=affiliazione_us&amp;utm_content=10&amp;utm_medium=affiliazione&amp;utm_source=linkshare_us&amp;tp=68585\">T by Alexander Wang</a> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">2009 年 7 月， Alexander Wang 推出全新的副线品牌 T by Alexander Wang 。与主线的风格比起来，副线更轻松，注重舒适和试穿性。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105452sihnaZULGKOgCIYk.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1538\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.42407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105452F2kQPDrpuiVedY9b.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1538\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.42407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021054530jC52cn9AMyfqzUo.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1538\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.42407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105453o4X0kPA5VMuIzU2F.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1538\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.42407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105453aUlEj1sf2H6counC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1538\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.42407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"